divs: Sighting DetailsI was about to take some food from my house when i saw the strange object hovering near the rooftop. It was low and moving slowly and sometimes it was moving fast. I was shocked and grab my camera. I also noticed some signal interruptions with our radio the same with some appliances like cellphone and television. i was scared especially when it hovers just above us. It just disappeared from a really great speed.
Summary: Large and metallic black and silver.
